{
    "_comment_policy": "--- Catalog policy: GGUF (k-quant) catalog served by llama.cpp on every platform (Windows / CPU-only Linux / low-VRAM GPUs / macOS without unified memory). Every shortcut points to a public, ungated HF repo and the resolver auto-selects the right .gguf file from the `:NNbit` suffix (see gguf_patterns_for_quant in src/model/resolver.rs — priority: UD-Q*_K_XL → Q*_K_M → Q*_K_S → Q*_K). The same key may appear in safetensors.json with a different repo for SGLang/AWQ pulls — that's intentional; each engine consults its own catalog. Publisher priority: unsloth (has Unsloth Dynamic UD- variants → best quality at same size) > Qwen-official (for embeddings/rerankers) > lmstudio-community (Qwen2.5 Instruct) > bartowski (Llama-70B + Qwen2.5-72B) > gpustack (BGE / Jina embed+rerank) > mradermacher (Qwen3 Reranker). ---",

    "_comment_qwen3": "--- Qwen 3 (April 2025). unsloth ships Q*_K_M + UD-Q*_K_XL for every size. `:4bit` → UD-Q4_K_XL > Q4_K_M, `:6bit` → UD-Q6_K_XL > Q6_K, `:8bit` → UD-Q8_K_XL > Q8_0. ---",
